{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Create a beautiful, modern price filter with range sliders for a collection page. The filter should have: dual range sliders for minimum and maximum price selection, smooth animations, premium design with elegant styling, real-time price display as user moves sliders, clean minimalist interface that matches a premium brand aesthetic, and responsive design. Make it visually appealing with modern UI elements instead of basic dropdown menus.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
